    <p class="requirements-para px-lg-5 mx-lg-5">In order to apply for a position at YTS, the following requirements must be met. After you've read the requirements, you can scroll down to see all the available roles and positions.</p>


    <div class="row my-5">
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card shadow bg-white rounded-lg border-0 mb-3">
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="media mb-3 align-items-center">
              <i class="requirements-icons requirements-linkedin fab fa-linkedin-in mr-3 bg-primary text-white rounded-circle"></i>
              <div class="media-body">
                <h5 class="mt-0 requirements-title-card">Applicants must have a LinkedIn profile</h5>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="card-text requirements-para-card">You must have a LinkedIn account before applying. During the application process, you will be required to insert the URL of your LinkedIn profile.</p>
            <a href="/faq" class="text-primary">Read why you need a LinkedIn <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ml-1"></i></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card shadow bg-white rounded-lg border-0 mb-3">
          <div class="card-body">
