              <div class="media-body">
                <h5 class="mt-0 requirements-title-card">Must be less than 23 years old.</h5>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="card-text requirements-para-card">All applicants must be below the age of 23. If you're 23 or older, you can still contribute to YTS in a variety of other ways. Click below to learn how.</p>
            <a href="/faq" class="text-primary">How can I contribute? <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ml-1"></i></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card shadow bg-white rounded-lg border-0">
          <div class="card-body">
